issue.title: Move blockstack interaction client-side
issue.body:
Client-side calls to getFile() and putFile() are necessary to interface with Gaia. This fix will involve:

- figuring out how to access datatransfer/data from the client
- figuring out how getFile() and putFile() work
- reworking what happens when the user presses "submit"
